      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hi, I'm on a local school board and we're trying to put together a formal policy regarding student cell phone use in classrooms. We need to balance student safety (being able to contact parents) with the need to stop distractions during lessons. Can you draft a policy for us? We'll need sections on permitted use, prohibited use, and what happens when the rules are broken.",
